NO CONTEST plea entered to count 1, PTC possess THC.  Convicted.
The State moves to dismiss and read in count 2.  Motion granted.
Sentence Withheld.  Defendant is placed on probation to DOC for twelve (12) months.
Conditions of probation:
1) Complete forty-five (45) hours of community service;
2) AODA assessment and follow through;
3) Submit to random urine screens and pay for same;
4) Assessment, treatment, counseling and deemed appropriate by the Departments assessment process;
5) Maintain fulltime employment, schooling or combination;
6) Pay court costs;
7) pay supervision fees in an amount to be determined by DOC;
8) Provide DNA sample.
Minutes.
